OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780427467
OL,3,CIsrael launches strikes on Lebanon
OL,4,Cdespite Trump's attempts to pause
OL,5,Cfighting
OL,7,FIsraeli drone strikes on southern
OL,8,FLebanon killed eight people, including
OL,9,Ftwo children, just a day after Donald
OL,10,FTrump said Israel and Hezbollah had
OL,11,Fagreed to dial back fighting.
OL,13,FDespite the announcement from Trump on
OL,14,FMonday, neither Hezbollah nor Israel
OL,15,Fappeared keen to stop their conflict
OL,16,Fon Tuesday.
OL,18,FHezbollah launches dozens of
OL,19,Fprojectiles towards Israeli soldiers
OL,20,Fand citizens on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
