CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780427467
OL,3,CIsrael launches strikes on Lebanon
OL,4,Cdespite Trump's attempts to pause
OL,5,Cfighting
OL,7,FThe ongoing fighting risks derailing
OL,8,FTrump's efforts to end the war with
OL,9,FIran, as Tehran has threatened to walk
OL,10,Faway from talks recently unless the
OL,11,Fconflict in Lebanon has ended.
OL,13,FIran has made the end of the conflict
OL,14,Fin Lebanon a key part of its
OL,15,Fnegotiations with the US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
