CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780427467
OL,3,CIsrael launches strikes on Lebanon
OL,4,Cdespite Trump's attempts to pause
OL,5,Cfighting
OL,7,FThe strikes come as a second round of
OL,8,Ftalks between Israel and Lebanon is
OL,9,Fscheduled for Tuesday and Wednesday in
OL,10,FWashington, where Lebanese negotiators
OL,11,Fare set to seek a full ceasefire that
OL,12,Fwill prevent future attacks.
OL,14,FThe talks began in April and were the
OL,15,Ffirst in more than three decades
OL,16,Fbetween the countries, which have no
OL,17,Fformal diplomatic relations. Hezbollah
OL,18,Fhas rejected direct talks, counting on
OL,19,Fpressure from Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780427468
OL,3,CIsrael launches strikes on Lebanon
OL,4,Cdespite Trump's attempts to pause
OL,5,Cfighting
OL,7,FThe planned talks come days after
OL,8,FIsraeli ground troops made their
OL,9,Fdeepest incursion into Lebanon in 26
OL,10,Fyears and Israel then threatened to
OL,11,Fstrike Beirut's southern suburbs,
OL,12,Fcausing panic in the Lebanese capital
OL,13,Fas thousands fled.
OL,15,FTrump said Monday he'd spoken with
OL,16,FIsraeli Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,17,FNetanyahu and had communicated with
OL,18,FHezbollah through mediators, and that
OL,19,Fno troops would be "going to Beirut".
OL,26,@{D@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
