PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780427468
OL,3,CIsrael launches strikes on Lebanon
OL,4,Cdespite Trump's attempts to pause
OL,5,Cfighting
OL,7,FIsraeli Defence Minister Israel Katz
OL,8,Fsaid on Tuesday that Israel previously
OL,9,Frefrained from attacking Beirut out of
OL,10,Fdeference for negotiations between the
OL,11,FUS and Iran.
OL,13,FHowever, he said Netanyahu had
OL,14,Finformed Trump in a phone call late on
OL,15,FMonday that Israel would attack
OL,16,FBeirut's southern suburbs if Hezbollah
OL,17,Fcontinued targeting northern Israel,
OL,18,Fechoing comments from the prime
OL,19,Fminister the previous day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
