OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780427468
OL,3,CIsrael launches strikes on Lebanon
OL,4,Cdespite Trump's attempts to pause
OL,5,Cfighting
OL,7,FAn Israeli drone strike hit a car on
OL,8,Fthe road linking the southern town of
OL,9,FMarjayoun with the city of Nabatiyeh,
OL,10,Fkilling James Karam, a dentist from
OL,11,Fthe nearby Christian town of Qlayaa,
OL,12,Falong with his daughter and son,
OL,13,FLebanon's state-run National News
OL,14,FAgency reported on Tuesday.
OL,16,FThey also reported that an Israeli
OL,17,Fairstrike on Monday killed six people
OL,18,Fin the southern village of Marwaniyeh.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
