OL,3,CIsrael launches strikes on Lebanon
OL,4,Cdespite Trump's attempts to pause
OL,5,Cfighting
OL,7,FHezbollah said on Tuesday its fighters
OL,8,Ffired anti-tank missiles on Israeli
OL,9,Ftroops who were pushing into the
OL,10,Fsouthern village of Hadatha, about
OL,11,Ffour miles from the Israeli border.
