OL,3,CIsrael launches strikes on Lebanon
OL,4,Cdespite Trump's attempts to pause
OL,5,Cfighting
OL,7,FSirens sounded in several areas in
OL,8,Fnorthern Israel, its military said in
OL,9,Fa statement. It added that "a
OL,10,Fsuspicious aerial target" was
OL,11,Fidentified in the area where Israeli
OL,12,Fsoldiers are operating in southern
OL,13,FLebanon, but that no injuries were
OL,14,Freported.
OL,16,FThe latest round of fighting between
OL,17,FIsrael and Hezbollah has killed 3,433
OL,18,Fpeople in Lebanon and displaced more
OL,19,Fthan a million people.
