OL,3,CIsrael launches strikes on Lebanon
OL,4,Cdespite Trump's attempts to pause
OL,5,Cfighting
OL,7,FAccording to Netanyahu's office, at
OL,8,Fleast 27 Israeli soldiers and a
OL,9,Fdefence contractor have been killed in
OL,10,For near southern Lebanon. Two
OL,11,Fcivilians have also been killed in
OL,12,Fnorthern Israel.
